    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12861#discussion_r3009715669\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Or, alternatively, just drop these entirely. I think this is the only use of <code>wasm_tag_t</code> (which also doesn't exist in C headers), so I think that type could be dropped too?</p>\n</blockquote>",
